Compression/Decompression Algorithmy himnvac e Huffman Codingi vra.
Nax stexcvum e textum exac bolor charactarneri aghysak vor cuyc e talis te yuraqanchyur character qani angam e handipel textum.
Stexcvum e Heap vortex pahvum e Node-ery`charactary ir hachaxutyamb.
Aynuhetev 2 aveli qich hachaxutyamb handipox charactarnery miavorvum en 1 Node-i mej` isk irenc hachaxutyunnery gumarvum.
Gorcoxutyuny katarvum e aynqan jamanak qani der Heapum ka 1 Nodic avel Node.
Processy verjanaluc heto stexcvum e Tree.
Tree-i dzax chyugin veragrvum e 0, isk Aj chyugin ` 1.
Ayspes amen mi Character stanum e ir Bitayin nerkayacumy.
Erb Character->Bit agyusaky patrastvum e, mnum e eghac informacian decode anel decompress anelu hamar